	    Please don't stone us! We are still working on it!

	    We search to do something worthy of the Amiga!

	    However, for those who are yelling that they are not
	yet able to insert new and beautiful Vocabulary terms, (I
	refer above all to the friends who have sent the
	shareware fee) who wish for us to make the VocUtente
	(most probably with a MUI interface) write to us and let
	us know exactly what kind of system you have, for
	example:

	    = type of Amiga
	    = how much extra RAM
	    = HardDisk
	    = accelerator
	    = if you have MUI installed

	    In other words, let us know what disk-drive you have
	(high or low density) and if you know how to
	use compression programs such as Lha, PowerPacker, etc.


