@NODE "Condizioni Distribuzione"

	    @{b}Conditions for distributing Ital:@{ub}

	    This program can be liberally copied and distributed
	freely.

	    A small fee may charged only for the disk and postage
	(no more, for example, than $5.00).

	    It may be included in any Public Domain/Shareware
	like "Fred Fish" and on any CoverDisk/CD dedicated to the
	Amiga.

	    It may also be uploaded to any BBS or Internet
	Server.

	    This program may not be compacted in any way except
	as noted below.

	    This program and its files are able to be
	distributed in the compressed form ONLY with .Lha, .Zip,
	.Arj, Lzx, or something compatible to them.

	    This manual, the program and all the other related files
	must be distributed together.

	    You may NOT modify the dictionary in any way!

	    As said above, distribution at no cost to the end user
	is accepted, but the code, algorythm, and all files
	remain legal property of the author.


@ENDNODE

